data.description: Step into luxury and comfort with this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spanning 2,555 sqft. Nestled on a scenic corner lot, the residence boasts a breathtaking water view on both the side and back, providing a tranquil backdrop to your daily life.    As you enter, be prepared to be captivated by the meticulous details and upgrades. The living space features real wood floors that exude warmth and sophistication, setting the tone for the entire home. Imagine entertaining guests in the impressive theater room, complete with built-in theater seats that offer the ultimate cinematic experience.    The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, adorned with stylish cement countertops that blend seamlessly with the modern aesthetic. Custom blinds and window treatments add an extra layer of elegance, allowing you to control the natural light that floods the space.    The home is not only aesthetically pleasing but also energy-efficient, thanks to the recently installed, fully paid-off solar panels and a new roof. Say goodbye to high utility bills and hello to sustainable living.    For those who enjoy the outdoors, the back of the home is a haven enclosed by a fully screened enclosure, creating a private retreat where you can unwind and enjoy the serene surroundings.    Completing the package is a practical 2-car garage, providing convenience and security for your vehicles. This residence seamlessly blends style, functionality, and eco-friendliness, offering a dream lifestyle in every square foot. Welcome home to the epitome of modern living.
